{"tid":681634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄媒：中國正加大對敘利亞的介入，不是動用軍隊，而是大量資金","createTime":"2018-05-28T08:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T14:41:04.000Z","uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"03e452e6188a24a1662b9b4d2ce729b878af1830","tid":681634,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:03:42.000Z","msg":"敘利亞的戰火正慢慢熄滅，但戰爭帶來的創傷卻是持久的。除了大量人員傷亡外，該國變成了一片廢墟。急需大量的重建資金。因西方制裁傷痕累累的俄國顯然拿不出這筆錢來，普京和阿薩德把目標投向了中國。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;今日俄羅斯&rdquo;於24日刊發文章稱，俄羅斯和伊朗無疑對阿薩德的軍隊贏得這場軍事戰爭至關重要。但現在，中國已經成為贏得和平的關鍵因素。中國可以將西方的破壞變成一個巨大的回報機會。譯文如下：<br />\n<br />\n中國正在加大對敘利亞的介入，而不是動用軍隊，而是大量資金。對北京來說，飽受戰爭蹂躪的敘利亞是投資的黃金機遇。而對於大馬士革，繁榮意味著和平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d.ifengimg.com/w600/p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0527/FB7B655902C76CC00D878E96D495B79E513E646B_size77_w780_h438.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd.ifengimg.com%2Fw600%2Fp0.ifengimg.com%2Fpmop%2F2018%2F0527%2FFB7B655902C76CC00D878E96D495B79E513E646B_size77_w780_h438.jpeg&h=8b21ae58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自中國的公司正在排隊等候，以贏得重建合同，包括城鎮\\村莊、道路、橋樑、學校、醫院和通訊網絡等等。這些設施被近7年的戰爭摧毀。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國估計，戰爭對敘利亞基礎設施造成的損失至少為2500億美元。中國可能是重建敘利亞的理想夥伴。俄羅斯和伊朗無疑對阿薩德的軍隊贏得這場軍事戰爭至關重要。但現在，中國已經成為贏得和平的關鍵因素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://wemedia.ifeng.com/62226333/wemedia.shtml?_cpb_remenwz3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwemedia.ifeng.com%2F62226333%2Fwemedia.shtml%3F_cpb_remenwz3&d=bFYDW4yt9lkxTqnDWxBjItibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3ae05761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://wemedia.ifeng.com/62226333/wemedia.shtml?_cpb_remenwz3</a>"},{"pid":"f3ba48d88ec018a22d7c2311db21c3f7ecbb7601","tid":681634,"uid":104699,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:07:26.000Z","msg":"化腐朽為神奇，唔關事都有得贏，邊個夠你小支支鬥啊屌，等去敍利亞食海底撈飲喜茶"},{"pid":"5f6b8691218b6cd17b6eb2793c5c21393de0ee61","tid":681634,"uid":60529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd156fd3a5dfdc223c45a121a408100ce80cb00","tid":681634,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"啫係邊個比錢？"},{"pid":"7dab29aa1b75d72a3768e4a48237700ad929309b","tid":681634,"uid":42921,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"擺明係俄大佬叫細佬俾錢"},{"pid":"47a1489385636a317499d934fd9f8d36d0b0ac86","tid":681634,"uid":81156,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"屌一諗到又有個國家要俾中共擰撚住個春袋就嬲"},{"pid":"61f86e5c146bda3168079245f780339e608c8e45","tid":681634,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:33:38.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cab3b2819c49f40e959af2a13fdb09c74e2369","tid":681634,"uid":45914,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:38:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6bb769ec484ed9cafe11b36a2feec31eab90b84","tid":681634,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47a1489385636a317499d934fd9f8d36d0b0ac86","tid":681634,"uid":81156,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"屌一諗到又有個國家要俾中共擰撚住個春袋就嬲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:39:28.000Z","msg":"本身敘利亞已經係俄羅斯睇場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee372e25c065e105fe86880252d2f747fb8b6ea9","tid":681634,"uid":57554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"借錢比敘利亞起，還唔到錢就要比中国起軍事基地，呢啲嘢佢係非洲做唔少啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdec79a70d2ac10bb3b710aafbca979f04cd7b5c","tid":681634,"uid":35468,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/164317_d0b3244693f7